<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Section Number="0583.06" xmlns="http://StatRev.xsd"><Catchline xml:space="preserve">Employment of assistants by department.</Catchline><SectionBody><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">The department may employ such assistants as are necessary to carry out and enforce the provisions of this chapter.</Text></SectionBody><History xml:space="preserve">s. 12, ch. 16982, 1935; CGL 1936 Supp. 4126(12); s. 2, ch. 61-119; ss. 14, 35, ch. 69-106; s. 9, ch. 84-102.</History></Section>